Chisom Faith Ezeh, popularly known as Rexxie, has acquired a magnificent house in Lagos. The popular music producer, sound engineer and entrepreneur who is known for being the originator of the current wave ‘Zanki Sound,” which is employed by several top music artistes and producers alike in making their music, is beyond ecstatic Rexxie shared several photos of the enviable home he acquired alongside a video on Instagram. Displaying his new home, he wrote: “It can only be God.”